SCENE 5  "CHRISTMAS PRESENT"
-------
(We don't want to bore you, so the second ghost came along, he was
less camp and talkative than the first, he just gobbed on Bill and
took him to a place full of PCs running Windows :( :( :( :( :( :(

U = Users (ordinary PC users - as they are commonly known)


BG - What did you bring me here for?
G  - To see the pain you're causing to the users.. Look! And gobs on
     Gates again.
BG - Why is he crying?  Moaned Bill wishing he'd worn rubber.
G  - Gobs again on Bates, Sighs and stares fixedly at the ceiling.
BG - Oh! I see, humffp, Win95 crashed and he lost all his work,
     too bad..
G  - Still staring upwards, gobs silently in a high arc accurately
     down Gates neck and then starts whistling quietly.
BG - Erm why is he laughing like a maniac? ... Mopping his neck half
     heartedly.
G  - Eyes like saucers, spraying spit everywhere and whistling more 
     shrill. 
BG - Hmm, His hard disk is full.. 2.5GB fULL !!!!!, It's not MY fault
     Windo..............Why is he hitting the keyboard with his head?
U  - Fucking asshole Bill Gates, it's been eight hours and still the
     fuckin' installation isn't finished!!!!.....
U1 - I don't understand why they have such huge demands on memory and
     CPU?
BG - Because it's a very good operating system... The ghost gobbed so
     hard this time Gates is knocked off his feet.
U  - Simply put, Billy-boy has it all his way. He forces the users to
     buy bigger hard disks, more memory, etc. He's taking all of us
     for fools!
U1 - The worst part is that everyone follows him..
BG - He he he, of course. He ducks too late, half a gallon of gob hits
     him square in the face.
G  - Fool. You don't understand a thing!.Let's go to a bookshop (whop)
BG - Ahaa! They're reading my book!
U  - Bill Gates is such an asshole!
BG - Hey! I've heard that before somewhere.
U1 - His book is the most lame thing I've ever read in my life! It's
     even worse than using DOS.
U  - He's writing as if he invented it all!
U1 - Yeah! He! Invented the internet, he! Gave multitasking to
     humanity..
U  - I bet it doesn't say that he tortured people for so many years
     with his fuckin'-DOS!
U1 - Why?... Do you think that in 2020 he'll write that he tortured
     people with Windows?
U  - IF he's still alive then he he he ...
U1 - Hahahahaha! Check this joke out: We've got Hitler, Saddam and
     Bill Gates in a room and a pistol with only two bullets, what do
     we do?
U  - Dunnow, What?
U1 - Shoot Bill Gates twice!
BG - Enough!, I say enough!!!
G  - Spitting accurately between each word.   OK, let's, go, for, a, 
     ride, to, your, corporation's, labs.. (Whop)


                        --- Commercial Break ---

A PEE CEE needs 8 times more ram than an AMIGA to do the same task ;).



(P1-P2 =  Micro$oft Programmers).

P1 - It's Christmas and I have to work for the Asshole.*
BG - grrrrr.. Gloop, another direct hit from the ghost.
P2 - Yeah, the fuckhead wants us to finish that fuckcode*


* =  These are talented programmers who once had dreams but ended up
     working for Bill Gates..


P1 - The Asshole has got on my nerves with that fuckin'compatibility
     of his.
P2 - And with that fuckin' DOS of his.
P1 - And those fuckin' features he ordered..
P2 - The Asshole has so much publicity that all those useless moron
