P1 - I'm finished, send it to some beta tester. I'm going home.. How
     about you?
P2 - I'm going to send an anonymous hate mail to Bill, he he he.....
BG - So THAT's who's been sending me anonymous mails for the last 2
     years.. My finest programmer!! Oh my God!!!. Gob cascades down
     his shirt front and oozes out of his navel.
G  - Look at the pain you're causing to the world! Don't you
     understand? This surprises Gates on two counts. 1, for the
     content and 2, because its gob free.
BG - No.. I'm tougher than Scrooge and I'm never going to change my
     tactics.. Leave me alone.. I want to sleep.
G  - Then go to sleep, he he he and wait for the third ghost.. He
     vanishes. (Whop).
BG - After a shower and change Billy boy climbs into bed, to find the
     ghost has filled it with gob....




SCENE 6  "CHRISTMAS FUTURE"
-------

(The third ghost even less talkative and subtle than the first two
simply wakes Bill with a resounding kick in the balls, grabs him by
the scruff of the neck and takes him to a computer shop circa
Christmas 2015).

BG - Managing to gasp out, If you start showing me scenes of my death
     to make me change my mind forget it. I won't change a thing..
G  - Releases his grip, drops Gates into some dog shit and says Look!!
BG - Stumbling to his feet, Where? At the shop? Oh !! We're in the
     year 2015 let's see what software is released. He strides
     towards the shop and a whiff of dog shit trails behind in his
     wake.
BG - Peers in through the shop front. Autocad86, Wordperfectxxi,
     Scalatl1000, ehm.. Strange, I don't see my company's mark
     anywhere.. Ghost, where are my products?
G  - He he he, I'll make you visible to humans for a while. Why don't
     you ask them..


                        --- Commercial Break ---

486 DX Pee Cee @ 66 MHz = AMIGA A4000 T @ 25 MHz he he he he he 
                                        --------




(Bill Gates steps into the shop and starts a conversation with the
shopkeeper).

S =  Shopkeeper

BG - Excuse me do you have Windows 2015?
S  - Haaahahahaha thank you sonny that made me laugh! And Sniffs
     suspiciously...
BG - Why? What did I say? Which Windows have you got? Which version?
S  - Aaaahahahaha please stop it, ahaha! .... Sniffs again and looks
     around with a puzzled expression on his face.
BG - Tell me, what happened to Windows?
S  - But son where have you been all these years? OK Sometime in 2000
     all the companies started fighting back, with the help of
     millions of angry users they started a new revolution.... Leans
     forward and sniffs again but gently this time.
BG - What do you mean?
S  - Masteros v1.0 came out. Then came 1.3 etc, then Corel and all the
     rest of those programs came out in versions for this OS, and the
     stocks of Microsoft fell to 20% in a year!. Leans back and frowns
     at Gates intently.
BG - Then what?
S  - Takes a deep breath and says, Then Apple started along with Amiga
     then came IBM with Motorola and they released brand new
     operating systems for a new generation of standard hardware.
     Microsoft kept losing ground, until in 2008 it crashed under its
     huge debts. He walks backward quickly, gagging.
BG - That can't be!
S  - Shouts at Gates from the opposite side of the shop, and all that
     wouldn't have happened if Bill Gates had listened to the world's
     negative comments.

Bill Gates, obviously disappointed, comes out of the shop and walks
over to the Ghost, offhand he notices a lot of dogs in the street.

BG - Ghost, er, can I change something?
G  - Grins wildly and hums to himself.

The dogs have formed a circle around Gates. Staring....

BG - Talk to me yells Gates, can I?
G  - Stops humming, Yes I should think so.... Time to go home..(Whop)


(The rest, goes like this)

Billy wakes up before Christmas and cancels the release of Windows97,
the world becomes a better place, and Amigatech releases Amigaos 5,
which gets 51% of software sales in the world. A multi platform
machine is released and competition is good for everybody, so they
lived happily ever after!

But what happened to the guest star?

Bill Gates entered a cryogenic unit. He'll wake up after 100 years to
see how his business is going. He he he he.
